node.text:
Giants.¹
cc: @dolphindronedom 

¹ From @dolphindronedom: “I think this is the biggest Humpback Whale I’ve ever seen in my life! I revisited this clip recently, and when I think how the average Pacific White-Sided Dolphin is typically 6-7 feet long, it’s AMAZING how tiny that is compared to this humongous Humpback! Humpbacks typically max out around 50ft long, and I believe this specimen was every bit of that…if not more! Humpbacks will become a more frequent sighting for us soon, peaking in October and November. As much as I love the Blues, it’s hard to beat the charismatic nature of a Humpback Whale!”
Amazing,  my dream to see in nature 😍😍
چقدر با عظمت و زیباست خیلی دوست دارم روزی از نزدیک این آبزی زیبا رو ببینم و باهاش خاطره ای زیبا داشته باشم در حضور در کنارش 🐋😍 وال بی نظیر
A M A Z I N G ! ! 😍
São baleia carnívora acho que a Baleia 🐋 tava tentando se proteger ou espantar elas de perto dos seus filhotes 😍

Giants.¹
cc: @dolphindronedom 

¹ From @dolphindronedom: “I think this is the biggest Humpback Whale I’ve ever seen in my life! I revisited this clip recently, and when I think how the average Pacific White-Sided Dolphin is typically 6-7 feet long, it’s AMAZING how tiny that is compared to this humongous Humpback! Humpbacks typically max out around 50ft long, and I believe this specimen was every bit of that…if not more! Humpbacks will become a more frequent sighting for us soon, peaking in October and November. As much as I love the Blues, it’s hard to beat the charismatic nature of a Humpback Whale!”
